    <p class="mb-4">
      Norway offers something unique: free tuition for everyone, including non-EU students. Combined with affordable healthcare (small copays, capped annually) and spectacular natural beauty, it's incredibly attractive—IF you can meet the financial requirements. The NOK 137,907 requirement is strictly enforced.
    </p>

    <p class="mb-4">
      The healthcare system is excellent once you're registered. Small copays are manageable, and the annual cap means costs are predictable. Register for your D-number immediately after arrival to access the system. Until then, ensure you have insurance.
    </p>

